OL,3,CDuke of Marlborough fined #500 for
OL,4,COxfordshire speeding offence
OL,6,FThe Duke of Marlborough has been fined
OL,7,F#500 after he was caught speeding in
OL,8,FOxfordshire.
OL,10,FCharles James Spencer-Churchill was
OL,11,Falso disqualified from driving for a
OL,12,Fperiod of 28 days, after admitting to
OL,13,Fspeeding at 80mph in a 50mph zone.
OL,15,FThe driving offence took place on
OL,16,FWoodstock Road, Yarnton, on October
OL,17,F18, 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
