OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778256667
OL,3,CDuke of Marlborough fined #500 for
OL,4,COxfordshire speeding offence
OL,6,FThe Duke - who is a relative of Sir
OL,7,FWinston Churchill and Diana, Princess
OL,8,Fof Wales - did not attend Friday's
OL,9,Fhearing at High Wycombe Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced in his absence, after
OL,13,Fhis solicitor entered a guilty plea on
OL,14,Fhis behalf.
OL,16,FDistrict Judge Kamlesh Rana told the
OL,17,Fcourt Spencer-Churchill had a "clean
OL,18,Fdriving record".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
