PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1778256667
OL,3,CDuke of Marlborough fined #500 for
OL,4,COxfordshire speeding offence
OL,6,FShe also imposed a #200 surcharge fee
OL,7,Fand #300 in prosecution costs as part
OL,8,Fof his sentence.
OL,10,FSpencer-Churchill was charged with
OL,11,Fanother count of failing to give
OL,12,Fpolice information, relating to the
OL,13,Fidentification of the driver of a
OL,14,FHyundai in Banbury, Oxfordshire,
OL,15,Fbetween November 15 and December 13,
OL,16,F2024.
OL,18,FBut the prosecution offered no
OL,19,Fevidence after Spencer-Churchill
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to the speeding charge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
